      "content": "\"Their very constitution speaks to their limitations; a brute strength without the refinement of intellect. Look at their customs—primitive rituals born of superstition, utterly devoid of the logical progression of true philosophy. They are children, gentlemen, magnificent in their wildness perhaps, but utterly incapable of grasping the intricate calculus of a modern state. We bring not just goods, but the very scaffolding of reason they are too inherently simple to construct for themselves.\"",
